cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

The paper deals with texture synthesis using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks for texture synthesis also involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the architecture of the neural networks used, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the visual quality of the synthesized textures, which could be considered under computer graphics (cs.GR).
